hadiths[37]{hadithnumber,text}:
1386,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hukm farmaya : '' qatl khata padhi. ki diyat padhi. bees bint makhaz padhi. , bees ibn makhaz , bees bint labun, bees juzaa, aur bees hiqa hai ''. hum ko abu-Hisham Rifaai ney ibne-Abi zyada aur abu-Khalid Ahmar sey aur unhoney Hujjaaj bin Irtaat sey isi tarah ki hadees bayan ki . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey marfoo jantey hain aur Abdullah bin Masood sey ye hadees maqoof tariqa sey bhi aai hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi maslak hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai, 4- ehle-ilm ka is baat par ittifaq hai ke diyat teen saal mein li jaeygi, har saal diyat ka tihai hissa liya jaeyga, 5- aur unka khayal hai ke diyate-khata usba par hai, 6- baaz logon key nazdik usba wo hain jo baap ki janib sey aadmi key qurbat daar hon , Malik aur Shafai ka yehi qol hai, 7- baaz logon ka kehna hai ke usba mein sey jo mard hain unhi par diyat hai, aurton aur bachon par nahin, un mein sey har aadmi ko chothai Dinar ka mukallaf banaya jaeyga, 8- kuch log kehtey hain : aadhey Dinar ka mukallaf banaya jaeyga, 9- agar diyat mukammal ho jaeygi to theek hai warna sab sey qaribi qabila ko dekha jaeyga aur in ko uska mukallaf banaya jaeyga."
1387,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney kisi momin ko jaan-bujh kar qatl kya usey maqtool key warison key hawaley kya jaeyga, agar wo chahen to usey qatl kar den aur chahen to us sey diyat lein , diyat ki miqdaar tees hiqa , tees juzaa aur chaalis Khalifa hai aur jis chiz par waris musaalihat kar lin wo unkey liye hai aur ye diyat key silsiley mein sakhti ki wajeh sey hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abdullah bin Amr ki hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1388,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney diyat baara hazar dirham muqarrar ki.
1389,"hum sey Sufiyan bin Uena ney Amr bin Dinar key wastey sey bayan kya, Amr bin Dinar ney ikrima sey aur ikrima ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat kya hai, lekin unhoney us riwayat mein ibne-Abbas ka zikr nahin kya, ibn Uena ki riwayat mein Muhammad bin Muslim Taaifii ki riwayat ki b-nisbat kuch ziyada baatein hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hamarey ilm mein Muhammad bin Muslim key ilawa kisi ney is hadees mein ''ibne-Abbas'' key wastey ka zikr nahin kya hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik usi hadees par amal hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai, 3- aur baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik diyat das hazar ( dirham ( hai, Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka yehi qol hai, 4- Imam Shafai kehtey hain : hum asal diyat sirf oont ko samajhtey hain aur wo so oont ya uski qeemat hai."
1390,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' « موضحہ » ( haddi khul janey waley zakham ( padhi. mein paanch oont hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- aur ehle-ilm key nazdik usi par amal hai, Sufiyan Sory, Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol yehi hai ke « موضحہ » ( haddi khul janey waley zakhm) mein paanch oont hain."
1391,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ungliyon ki diyat key barey mein farmaya : '' dono haath aur dono pair barabar hain, ( diyat mein) har ungli key badley das oont hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad sey ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan sahih aur gharib hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai, Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya isi key qaail hain."
1392,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' diyat mein ye aur ye barabar hain, yani chhanguli ya angutha''۔"
1393,"eik quraishi ney eik Ansari ka daant tod diya, Ansari ney Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey fariyad ki, aur un sey kaha : ameerul-momeneen! us (quraishi) ney mera daant tod diya hai, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : hum tumhen zarur razi kerengey, doosrey (yani quraishi) ney Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey bada israr kya aur) yahan tak mannat-samajat ki ke) unhen tang kar diya, Muawiya us sey mutmain na huye, chunanche Muawiya ney us sey kaha : tumhara maamla tumharey sathi key haath mein hai, Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) unkey paas bethey huye they, Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko kehtey suna hai, merey kanon ney isey suna hai aur dil ney isey mehfooz rakha hai, aap farma rahey they : '' jis aadmi key bhi jism mein zakham lagey aur wo usey sadqa kar dey (yani maaf kar dey) to Allah Taala usey eik darja bulandi ata karta hai aur uska eik gunah maaf farma deta hai, Ansari ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aap ney suna hai? Abu-Darda ney kaha : merey dono kanon ney suna hai aur merey dil ney isey mehfooz rakha hai, usney kaha : to main uski diyat maaf kar deta hun, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : lekin main tumhen mehroom nahin karunga , chunanche unhoney usey kuch maal deney ka hukm diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hamen ye sirf isi sanad sey malum hai, mujhey nahin malum ke abu-Safar ney Abu-Darda sey suna hai, 2- abu-Safar ka naam Saeed bin Ahmed hai, unhen ibne-Yuhmid Sory bhi kaha jata hai."
1394,"eik ladki zewar pehney huye kahin janey key liye nikli , eik Yahudi ney isey pakad kar pathar sey uska sar kuchal diya aur uskey paas jo zewar they wo us sey chheen liya , phir wo ladki aisi haalat mein pai gaee ke is mein kuch jaan baqi thi, chunanche usey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas laya gaya, aap ney us sey puchha : '' tumhen kis ney maara hai, falan ney ? '' usney sar sey ishara kya : nahin, aap ney puchha : '' falan ney ? '' yahan tak ke us Yahudi ka naam liya gaya ( jisney uska sar kuchla tha ( to usney apney sar sey ishara kya yani haan ! to Yahudi pakda gaya, aur usney aetraafe-jurm kar liya , phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hukm diya, aur uska sar do patharon key darmiyan kuchal diya gaya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur ehle-ilm key nazdik isi par amal hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : qisaas sirf talwaar sey liya jaeyga."
1395,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' duniya ki barbadi Allah key nazdik eik musalman key qatl honey sey kahin ziyada kamtar o aasan hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum sey Muhammad bin Bashaar ney basanad (محمد بن جعفر حدثنا شعبة an يعلى بن عطاء an أبيه an عبد الله بن عمرو) isi tarah riwayat ki hai, lekin unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya hai, 2- ye riwayat ibne-Abi Adi ki riwayat key bilmuqabil ziyada sahih hai (yani moquf hona ziyada sahih hai), 3- Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ko ibne-Abi Adi ney Shoba sey , basanad (يعلى بن عطاء an أبيه an عبد الله بن عمرو an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi tarah riwayat kya hai, jabke Muhammad bin Jaafar aur unkey ilawa dusron ney Shoba sey basanad «Yaala bin Ata» riwayat kya hai, lekin unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya hai, isi tarah Sufiyan Sory ney Yala bin Ata sey moqufan riwayat ki hai aur ye (moqoof riwayat ibne-Abi Adi ki) marfoo hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, 4- is bab mein Saad, ibne-Abbas , abu-Saeed , Abu-Hurera , Aqba bin Aamir , ibne-Masood aur Barida (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1396,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' (aakhirat mein) bandon key darmiyan sab sey pehley khoon key barey mein faisla kya jaeyga '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, isi tarah kaee logon ney Aamash sey marfooan riwayat ki hai, 2- aur baaz ney Aamash sey riwayat ki hai un logon ney isey marfoo nahin kaha hai."
1397,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' (aakhirat mein) bandon key darmiyan sab sey pehley khoon ka faisla kya jaeyga ''.
1398,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar aasman aur zamin waley ( sarey key sarey (eik momin key khoon mein mulawwis ho jaeyn to Allah un ( sab ( ko ondhey munh jahannam mein dal dega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai.
1399,"mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya , ( to dekha (ke aap baap ko betey sey qisaas dilwatay they aur betey ko baap sey qisaas nahin dilwatay they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Suraqa (Raziallahu anhu) ki is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. iski sanad sahih nahin hai, isey Ismail bin Ayash ney Musanna bin Sabaah sey riwayat ki hai aur Musanna bin Sabaah hadees mein zaeef gardaney jatey hain, 2- is hadees ko abu-Khalid Ahmar ney b-tareeq : (عن الحجاج بن أرطاة an عمرو بن شعيب an أبيه an جده an عمر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat kya hai, 4- ye hadees Amr bin Shuaib sey mursalan bhi marvi hai, is hadees mein iztirab hai, 4- ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai ke baap jab apney betey ko qatl kar dey to badley mein) قصاصاً ( usey qatl nahin kya jaeyga aur jab baap apney betey par) zina ki) tohmat lagaey to is par had qazaf nafiz nahin hogi ."
1400,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' baap sey betey ka qisaas nahin liya jaeyga''۔
1401,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''masjidon mein hudood nahin qaaim ki jaeyngi aur betey key badley baap ko) qisaas mein) qatl nahin kya jaeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is sanad sey is hadees ko hum sirf Ismail bin Muslim ki riwayat sey marfoo jantey hain aur Ismail bin Muslim makki key hifz key silsiley mein baaz ehle-ilm ney kalam kya hai.
1402,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi musalman shakhs ka khoon jo is baat ki gawahi deta ho ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur main Allah ka Rasool hun, halal nahin siwaye teen baaton mein sey kisi eik key : ya to wo shaadi shuda zaani ho, ya jaan ko jaan key badley maara jaey, ya wo apna Deen chhod kar jamaate-muslemeen sey alag ho gaya ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Usman , Aaisha aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1403,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' khabardar! jisney kisi aisey zimmi ko qatl kya jisey Allah aur uskey Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki panah hasil thi to usney Allah key ehad ko tod diya, lihaza wo jannat ki khushbu nahin paa sakega, halanke uski khushbu sattar saal ki masafat ( doori) sey aayegi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Abu-Hurera ki hadees kaee sanadon sey marvi hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1404,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney qabila Aamir key do aadmiyon ko musalmanon key barabar diyat di, ( kyonkey ( un dono ka Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ehad o paiman tha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, usey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- hadees key Raavi abu-Saad baqaal ka naam Saeed bin Mirzban hai."
1405,"jab Allah ney apney Rasool key liye Makka ko Fateh kar diya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon mein khadey ho kar Allah ki hamd o sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : '' jis ka koi shakhs maara gaya ho usey do baaton mein sey kisi eik ka ikhtiyar hai : ya to maaf kar dey ya ( qisaas mein) usey qatl karey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai) کماسیأتی ( , padhi. 2- is bab mein Wayl bin Hajar , Anas , abu-Shuraih aur khuwelid bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1406,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Makka ko Allah ney hurmat wala ( mohtaram ( banaya hai, logon ney isey nahin banaya , pas jo shakhs Allah aur youme-aakhirat par eman rakhta ho wo is mein khoonrezi na kerey. na uska darkht kaatey , ( ab ( agar koi ( khoonrezi key liye) is daleel sey rukhsat nikaley ke Makka Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key liye halal kya gaya tha (to uska ye istidlaal batil hai) isliye ke Allah ney isey merey liye halal kya tha logon key liye nahin, aur merey liye bhi din key eik khas waqt mein halal kya gaya tha, phir wo qiyamat tak haram hai? aey Khuza-aa walo ! tum ney huzail key us aadmi ko qatl kya hai, mein uski diyat ada karney wala hun, ( sun lo ( aaj key baad jis ka bhi koi aadmi maara jaeyga to maqtool key warison ko do chizon mein sey kisi eik ka ikhtiyar hoga : ya to wo ( uskey badley ( usey qatl kar den , ya us sey diyat ley lein ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees bhi Hasan sahih hai, 2- usey Sheban ney bhi Yahya bin abi Kasir sey usi key misl riwayat kya hai, 3- aur ye (hadees banam abu-Shuraih kaabi ki jagah banam) abu-Shuraih khuzaee bhi riwayat ki gaee hai. (aur ye dono eik hi hain (aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, aap ney farmaya : '' jis ka koi aadmi maara jaey to usey ikhtiyar hai ya to wo uskey badley usey qatl kar dey , ya maaf kar dey , ya diyat wasul karey '' 4- baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai."
1407,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney main eik aadmi qatl kar diya gaya, to qatil maqtool key wali) waris ( key supurd kar diya gaya, qatil ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! mainey usey qasdan qatl nahin kya hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' khabrdar ! agar wo ( qatil (apney qol mein sacha hai phir bhi tum ney isey qatl kar diya to tum jahannam mein jaaogey'', chunanche maqtool key wali ney isey chhod diya, wo aadmi rassi sey bandha huwa tha, to wo rassi ghaseet'ta huwa bahar nikla , isliye uska naam ذوالنسعہ ( rassi ya tasmey wala ( rakh diya gaya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur « نسعہ » : rassi ko kehtey hain."
1408,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kisi lashkar par ameer muqarrar kar key bhejtey to khas taur sey usey apney barey mein Allah sey darney ki wasiyat farmatey , aur jo musalman uskey sath hotey unhen bhalai ki wasiyat kartey , chunanche aap ney farmaya : '' Allah key naam sey uskey raastey mein jihad karo, jo kufr karey us sey lado , jihad karo, magar maale-ghanimat mein khayanat na karo, bad-ehdi na karo, musla  na karo aur na kisi bachey ko qatl karo'', hadees mein kuch tafsil hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Barida ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , Shaddad bin Aus , Imran bin Husain , Anas , Samra , Mughira , Yala bin Murra aur abu-Ayyub sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ney musla ko haram kaha hai."
1409,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' beshak Allah ney har kaam ko achey tareeqey sey karna zaruri qarar diya hai, lihaza jab tum qatl padhi. karo to achey tareeqey sey qatl karo, aur jab tum zibeh karo to achey tareeqey sey zibeh karo, tumharey har aadmi ko chahiye ke apni chhuri tez kar ley aur apney zabiha ko aaram pahunchaey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1410,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney « جنين » ( hamal ( ki diyat mein «gharra» yani ghulam ya laundi ( deney (ka faisla kya, jis key khilaf faisla kya gaya tha wo kehney laga : kya aisey ki diyat di jaeygi, jisney na kuch khaya na piya , na cheekhaa , na aawaz nikali , is tarah ka khoon to zaya aur batil ho jata hai, ( ye sun kar) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ye shaairon wali baat kar raha hai padhi. , « جنين » ( hamal gira deney ( ki diyat mein «Gharra» yani ghulam ya laundi dena hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Hamal bin Malik bin naabgha aur Mughira bin Shoba sey ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, 4- gharra ki tafseer baaz ehle-ilm ney , ghulam , londi ya paanch so dirham sey ki hai, 5- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : «Gharra» sey murad ghoda ya khachar hai."
1411,"do aurten saukan thin, un mein sey eik ney dusri ko pathar ya khemey ki mekh (khoonti) sey maara , to uska hamal saaqit ho gaya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us hamal ki diyat mein «gharra» yani ghulam ya laundi deney ka faisla farmaya aur diyat ki adaegi us aurat key usba key zimma thehrai. Hasan Basri kehtey hain : Zaid bin Hubab ney Sufiyan Sory sey riwayat ki, aur Sufiyan Sory ney Mansoor sey is hadees ko isi tarah riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1412,"mainey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha kya padhi. : ameerul-momeneen! kya aap key paas kaghaz mein likhi hui koi aisi tehreer hai jo Quran mein nahin hai? unhoney kaha : nahin, us zaat ki qism jisney daney ko phada aur jaan ko paida kya ! main siwaye us faham o baseerat key jisey Allah Taala Quran key silsiley mein aadmi ko nawazta hai aur us saheefey mein mojud chiz key kuch nahin janta , mainey puchha : saheefa mein kya hai? kaha : is mein diyat , qaidiyon key azad karney ka zikr aur aap ka ye farman hai : '' momin kafir key badley qatl nahin kya jaeyga '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik isi par amal hai, Sufiyan Sory, Malik bin Anas, Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, ye log kehtey hain : momin kafir key badley nahin qatl kya jaeyga, 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : zimmi key badley bator qisaas musalman ko qatl kya jaeyga, lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
1413,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' musalman kafir key badley qisaas mein qatl nahin kya jaeyga'', aur isi sanad sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kafir ki diyat momin ki diyat ka nisf hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- Yahudi aur nasrani ki diyat mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, Yahudi aur nasrani ki diyat ki baabat baaz ehle-ilm ka maslak Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hadees key muwaafiq hai, 3- umr bin abdul-Azeez kehtey hain : Yahudi aur nasrani ki diyat musalman ki diyat ka nisf hai, Ahmed bin Hanbal isi key qaail hain."
1414,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo apney ghulam ko qatl kerega hum bhi usey qatl kar dengey aur jo apney ghulam ka kaan, naak kaatega hum bhi uska kaan, naak kaatengey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi maslak hai, Ibrahim Nakhai isi key qaail hain, 3- baaz ehle-ilm maslan Hasan Basri aur ata bin abi Ribah waghera kehtey hain : azad aur ghulam key darmiyan qisaas nahin hai, (na qatl karney mein, na hi qatl sey kam zakhm pahunchaney) mein , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : agar koi apney ghulam ko qatl kar dey to uskey badley usey qatl nahin kya jaeyga, aur jab doosrey key ghulam ko qatl kerega to usey uskey badley mein qatl kya jaeyga, Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka yehi qol hai."
1415,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they : diyat ki adaeygi aaqila padhi. par hai, aur biwi apney shohar ki diyat sey meeras mein kuch nahin paey gi, yahan tak ke in ko Suhak bin Sufiyan kilaabi ney bataya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen eik farman likha tha : '' Ashim Zababi ki biwi ko uskey shohar ki diyat sey meeras do''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1416,"eik aadmi ney eik aadmi ka haath kaat khaya , usney apna haath khincha to daant kaatney waley key dono agley daant toot gaey, wo dono Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas apna maamla ley gaey to aap ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey koi apney bhai ko oont key kaatney ki tarah kaat khata hai, tumharey liye koi diyat nahin, phir Allah ney ye aayat nazil ki : (والجروح قصاص) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Yala bin Umayya aur Salma bin Umayya Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain aur ye dono bhai hain."
1417,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik aadmi ko tohmat padhi. ki bina par qaid kya, phir (ilzam Sabit na honey par) usko riha kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- Behaz bin Hakim bin Muawiya bin Haida Qusheri ki hadees jisey wo apney baap sey aur wo unkey dada sey riwayat kartey hain, Hasan hai, 3- Ismail bin Ibrahim ibne-Uleh ney Behaz bin Hakeem sey ye hadees us sey ziyada mukammal aur lambi riwayat ki hai."
1418,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo apney maal ki hifazat kartey huye maara jaey wo shaheed hai padhi. aur jisney eik baalisht bhi zamin churaai qiyamat key din usey saat zaminon ka toq pehnaya jaeyga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is hadees mein Hatim bin Siyah Maruzi ney izafa kya hai, Maamar kehtey hain : Zohri sey mujhey hadees pahunchi hai, lekin mainey un sey nahin suna ke unhoney is hadees yani (من قتل دون ماله فهو شهيد) '' jo apney maal ki hifazat kartey huye maara jaey wo shaheed hai'' mein kuch izafa kya ho, isi tarah Shuaib bin abu-Hamza ney ye hadees b-tareeq : (الزهري an طلحة بن عبد الله an عبدالرحمٰن بن عمرو بن سهل an سعيد بن زيد an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai, neez Sufiyan bin Uena ney b-tareeq : (الزهري an طلحة بن عبد الله an سعيد بن زيد an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai, is mein Sufiyan ney Abdur-Rehman bin Amr bin Sehal ka zikr nahin kya."
1419,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo apney maal ki hifazat kartey huye maara jaey wo shaheed hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai, ye dusri sanadon sey bhi un sey marvi hai 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney aadmi ko apni jaan o maal ki hifazat key liye difaa ki ijazat di hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Ali, Saeed bin Zaid, abu-Huraira, ibne-Umar, ibne-Abbas aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain : aadmi apney maal ki hifazat key liye difaa karey chahey uska maal do dirham hi kyon na ho."
1420,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis aadmi ka maal nahaq chheena jaey aur wo uski hifazat key liye difaa karta huwa maara jaey to wo shaheed hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. is sanad sey bhi Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas Raziallahu anhuma ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai.
1421,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''jo apney maal ki hifazat kartey huye qatl kya jaey wo shaheed hai, jo apney Deen ki hifazat kartey huye qatl kya jaey wo shaheed hai, jo apni jaan ki hifazat ki khatir maara jaey wo shaheed hai aur jo apney ehal o ayaal ki hifazat kartey huye qatl kya jaey wo shaheed hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Ibrahim bin Saad sey kaee raawiyon ney usi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai."
1422,"Abdullah bin Sehal bin Zaid aur Mahisa bin Masood bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma kahin janey key liye ghar sey rawana huye, jab wo khaibar pahunchey to alag-alag raaston par ho gaey, phir Mahisa ney Abdullah bin Sehal ko maqtool paya , kisi ney in ko qatl kar diya tha, aap ney unhen dafna diya, phir wo ( yani Raavi hadees ( Huwesa bin Masood aur Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huye, Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal un mein sab sey chhotey they, wo apney dono sathiyon sey pehley (us maamley mein aap sey) baat karna chahtey they, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''badey ka lihaz karo, lihaza wo khamosh ho gaey aur unkey dono sathiyon ney guftgu ki, phir wo bhi un dono key sath shareek-e-guftgu ho gaey, un logon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Abdullah bin Sehal key qatl ka waqia bayan kya, aap ney un sey farmaya : '' kya tum log pachas qasmen khaaogey (ke fulan ney usko qatl kya hai) taake tum apney sathi key khoon baha key mustahiq ho jaao (ya kaha) qatil key khoon key mustahiq ho jaao?'' un logon ney arz kya : hum qism kaisey khaeyn jabke hum hazir nahin they? aap ney farmaya : '' to Yahud pachas qasmen kha kar tum sey bari ho jaeyngey'', un logon ney kaha : hum kafir qom ki qism kaisey qubul kar lein ? phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jab ye maamla dekha to un ki diyat padhi. khud ada kar di. is sanad sey bhi Sehal bin abu Hasma aur Raafey bin khadeej sey isi tarah usi maana ki hadees marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Qasama key silsiley mein baaz ehle-ilm ka usi hadees par amal hai, 3- Madina key baaz fuqaha Qasama padhi. ki bina par qisaas durust samajhtey hain, 4- koofa key baaz ehle-ilm aur kuch doosrey log kehtey hain : Qasama ki bina par qisaas wajib nahin, sirf diyat wajib hai."
